                                <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-1 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">The CSS Box Model</h1>
                                <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">Understand the fundamental concept that governs layout on the web. Every element is a rectangular box!</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="aspect-video w-full rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-gray-200 dark:bg-white/10">
